NOMADAO

OUR PROJECTS

MetaBooking

Our 3D vizualization solution helps hotels display their rooms, spas, and restaurants in amazing 3D detail. Customers can easily see what their stay will look like and conveniently pay and book within the platform.

NomadVerse

Experience a new level of virtual reality with our Unreal Engine 5 technology! Hotels can offer visitors exciting games, challenges, digital tours, concerts, and virtual services. Give your visitors an unforgettable experience with our innovative solution.

NomadAI

Analytic and forecasting tool used by the community members to optimize hotel pricing and capitalize on underprices assets.

NomadPay

We've created a digital currency exchange that allows hotels and travelers to make cross-border payments quickly and affordably. No middlemen, no high fees, and no hassle.

NomadPerson

We offer a solution to turn personal and corporate brands into digital assets (tokens), which can be used to build communities and generate new streams of revenue.

CashLink

We provide a tool to manage funds, digital assets, bookings, and personal accounts for ambassadors, agents, and community members in the Nomad Ecosystem.

ABOUT US

NomaDao is the world's first decentralized meta-booking platform, changing the way we exchange goods and services in the travel industry. Our ecosystem allows for limitless exploration and discovery, all while using blockchain technology for security and transparency. Join us to unlock new opportunities and uncover hidden gems from around the world.
